The paper discusses the deployment of AI models in the healthcare industry, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the performance analysis of different hardware configurations, which is related to Machine Learning (cs.LG). The healthcare domain constraints are also discussed, which falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the use of GPU accelerators, which is related to Augmented Reality (cs.AR) and Computer Vision (cs.CV).
